@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f79ed0e4be9fc2fe3e9a8fdf208e353645ea6f6","tid":920309,"uid":153689,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T22:09:53.000Z","msg":"唔知點解諗起早排睇嘅marvel漫畫<br />\n紅骷髏利用宇宙魔方改寫過去，將美國隊長變成九頭蛇嘅忠實信徒。<br />\n結果美國隊長上左位之後就將紅骷髏收皮，原因好似係佢覺得紅骷髏偏離左九頭蛇嘅宗旨/紅骷髏阻礙左九頭蛇發展之類。<br />\n睇返依篇新聞，如果真係搞個「超級黨性」嘅改造人。我驚到時候改造人第一個要對付嘅就係依家依班高層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"736a34479437174260d29fd5b880deb538987cfd","tid":920309,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af9ef45ccd27a341eac60b6ed3def9704eb164ef","tid":920309,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a961d986d1b376f3e69cdfb932b75a6ff1f2b7ee","tid":920309,"uid":18552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T17:35:59.000Z","msg":"都預撚左係咁<br />\n<br />\n不過最係個段先好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T19:00:13.000Z","msg":"最「係個」段？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:04:54.000Z","msg":"最後"},{"pid":"a5eebad8b6ffaebf6dc1565bca8e188d5bf2b7e9","tid":920309,"uid":66686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T01:12:33.000Z","msg":"原文來源？"},{"pid":"968c85d2e8866e20d025948632f46194a9de8bc3","tid":920309,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:17:19.000Z","msg":"大君主之役入面既不死士兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f54e11e28edd353bdd17b38443541c59e389e3","tid":920309,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:19:36.000Z","msg":"老大哥？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}